title: 260 - The Missing Peace
description: This week, in the spirit of the Holiday Season, the guys are joined by nationally syndicated radio personality, activist, actor, & musician, Willie Moore Jr., who engages in a candid and moving dialogue about his life’s journey including being adopted at the age of three months, his journey as an R&B/Hip-Hop artist, rejection from his biological mother, hitting rock bottom financially, and ultimately his rise to the success that he experiences today.
